Slackware-Live is a live CD/DVD/USB build and install tool 
written for Slackware Linux:
- contains all the necessary to convert an installed system to a 
live system and vice-versa; includes an installation program with GUI;
- ability to build a system from packages;
- it doesn't need any kernel recompile;
- no changes are needed on the system to make live;
- support multiple SquashFS modules;
- can run in RAM.

LiNomad is an customized boot solution (optional) with the following features:
- fast startup and shutdown;
- support for home directory on USB (nomad system);
- support for GUI auto-detection and auto-login.
